<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-11-26T05:23:08-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-11-26T05:23:08-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-26T05:23:08-05:00</updated><title>三星曲线旗舰 Galaxy S25 Ultra 的视频泄露</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8Rdb4OXkUtT_edpMXY1tEyzTSBo=/0x34:1067x745/1310x873/cd n.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73748108/Samsung_Galaxy_S25_Ultra_video_leak.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;泄露的 Galaxy S25 Ultra 的边缘看起来比当前的 S24 Ultra 旗舰产品要柔和得多。&lt;/em>; |图片：&lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/samsunggalaxy/comments/1gzlim3/s24_ultra_definitely&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;1gzlim3 / Reddit&lt;/a>;&lt;/figcaption >; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;LIyPsX&quot;>;三星 Galaxy S25 系列预计将于 2025 年初推出，但新款泄漏让我们很好地了解了它会是什么样子。一段标题为“绝对是 S24 Ultra”&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/samsunggalaxy/comments/1gzlim3/s24_ultra_definitely&quot;>;发布在 Reddit 上的视频&lt;/a>;的误导性视频，确定是 Galaxy S25 Ultra通过 &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/universeice/status/1861228995993546832&quot;>;可靠的泄密者Ice Universe&lt;/a>;，展示了三星当前旗舰智能手机上没有的圆角，支持了之前的泄密和谣言。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;8QSelU&quot;>;圆角也呼应了即将推出的 &lt;a 中的圆形 UI 元素href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/26/24206755/samsung-galaxy-one-ui-7-revealed-leak&quot;>;三星即将发布的一个 UI 7 软件更新&lt;/a>;推出。动手视频中看到的其他功能包括光滑的表面、金属般的边缘和三星可识别的后置摄像头设置——所有这些也可以在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/jukanlosreve/status/ 1859187280264695898&quot;>;疑似 Galaxy S25 Ultra 假机泄露...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/26/24306324/samsung-galaxy-s25-ultra-video-leak&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/26/24306324/samsung-galaxy-s25-ultra-video-leak" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/26/24306324/samsung-galaxy-s25-ultra-video-leak</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-25T23:10:01-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-25T23:10:01-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2024 年节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片，色彩鲜艳的礼物散落在充满活力的图案纸的图形背景上。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jn5vPGijZj_9jMXWlJje3eVdaJ8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cd n.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73709099/247215_Holiday_GG_2024_AKrales_MAIN_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;一系列有趣、实惠且独特的礼物，适合您清单上的每个人。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24224043/holiday-gift-guide-2024-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24224043/holiday-gift-guide-2024-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24224043/holiday-gift-guide-2024-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>边缘人员</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-25T22:08:38-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-25T22:08:38-05:00</updated><title>美国诉谷歌 redux：广告技术审判的所有新闻</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一组正义秤在各种产品广告的背景前。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-eQHjIdTQNVInC21LbpW5OozcZU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cd n.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73573747/STK445_ADVERTISING_STK093_GOOGLE_F.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge、Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;谷歌和政府最近结束了他们的搜索反垄断案件，最终法官认定谷歌是垄断者。&lt; /p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237832/google-monopoly-trial-ad-tech-antitrust-us-search&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24237832/google-monopoly-trial-ad-tech-antitrust-us-search" rel="a